  • Must-edges form a cycle             → -1
  • Graph is disconnected               → -1
  • All must-edges, no optionals        → check cycle, return min(must strengths)
  • k=0, no upgrades                    → standard max-min spanning tree
  • k ≥ E, unlimited upgrades           → upgrade every optional edge you pick
